high_descs: Go to the table across the room
Pick up the knife near the egg
Turn left and go to the sink behind you
Put the knife in the sink
Take the martini glass from the sink
Turn around and face the counter
Put the martini glass on the counter
anns.task_desc: Taking items in and out of the sink

high_descs: Go to the white dishwasher, turn left, go to the green central counter, and turn left to face the green central counter.
Pick up the silver butter knife from the green central counter.
Turn around and go to the sink.
Put the silver butter knife in the glass in the sink.
Take the silver butter knife and the glass from the sink.
Turn around and face the white oven.
Put the silver butter knife and the glass on the green counter to the left.
anns.task_desc: Put a butter knife inside a glass on the counter over the dishwasher.

high_descs: Walk forward then turn left to face the green table.
Pick up the knife by the egg.
Turn around to face the sink.
Put the knife inside the glass that is in the sink.
Pick up the glass with the knife inside.
Turn a full circle to face the stove.
Place the glass with the knife inside on the counter top, above the dishwasher, to your left.
anns.task_desc: Put the glass with the knife inside on the counter top.
